original_title: Astro the Wonderdog Saves the World
overview: The epic 1988 B Grade Classic - a lost and hungry alien crashes in a remote desert region of Wisconsin due to retro turbo phasar problems...where will he go, who will he find, and has he had his lunch yet?
tagline: Where will he go, who will he find, and has he had his lunch yet?
title: Astro the Wonderdog Saves the World
